Package: continuonbrain
Version: 1.0.0
Section: science
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), python3-venv, python3-pip, chromium-browser | google-chrome-stable, swig, liblgpio-dev, i2c-tools, systemd, openbox, lightdm, unclutter, curl
Recommends: ssh
Maintainer: ContinuonAI <support@continuonai.com>
Description: Robotic AI Brain with Web Interface
 ContinuonBrain provides a complete AI-powered robotic control system
 with web-based management interface. Boots directly to kiosk mode.
 .
 Features:
  - Web-based robot management UI
  - AI-powered control with Gemma 3N VLM
  - HOPE brain architecture for learning
  - Automatic hardware detection
  - Kiosk mode for appliance-like experience
  - Developer mode for advanced users
